      "title": "Simulation-based crisis resource management training for pediatric critical care medicine: a review for instructors",
      "abstract": "Objective:To review the essential elements of crisis resource management and provide a resource for instructors by describing how to use simulation-based training to teach crisis resource management principles in pediatric acute care contexts.Data Source:A MEDLINE-based literature source.Outline of"
